attributes.description: Sunrise across Principal Valley to signify a new light and journey
Elves possess unparalleled quartz craftsmanship, through which they imbue their weapons with eternal sharpness
Exposure to the red arid soil of the Bullish Valleys has made the skin of each new generation become slightly more pink
Light clothing, good for fast travel. Its red color is obtained from the leaves of Copium plants, commonly found on the Bearish Mountains
The freedom of not having hair allows one to be more productive with their day
Those who don’t smile are their own harshest critics
An elf is not quick to anger, so be wary of their consternation
Dark eyes are better for not drawing attention and capture more detail in the night
Woven by the owner's magic, it imbues a fragment of the Wizard's soul. Blue represents its creator's depth of knowledge
The latest research and innovation allows the wearer to ascertain another’s power level
